# Python build / cache artifacts
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Test / coverage / type-check caches
.coverage
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.hypothesis/

# Local runtime databases (durable store / audit DB)
.secugent/*.db
.secugent/*.db-shm
.secugent/*.db-wal

# Default run-state / lease sqlite location (OrchestratorConfig.run_state_db_path
# defaults to data/run_state.db; the W1 boot wiring upgrades prod's in-memory
# default to a durable sqlite store here). Runtime data, never committed.
data/

# Environment secret files — NEVER commit real secrets. deploy/.env.example
# tells operators to `cp .env.example .env` and fill in real POSTGRES_PASSWORD
# / VAULT_TOKEN / ANTHROPIC_API_KEY / GRAFANA_PASSWORD, so the resulting .env
# must stay out of history (SECURITY_CONTRACT §6 / §10.6). The negation keeps
# the *.example templates tracked.
**/.env
!**/.env.example
# DA-M11: the Prometheus scrape bearer (deploy/prometheus/metrics_token) holds
# the SAME secret as SECUGENT_METRICS_TOKEN; keep it out of history. The tracked
# template (metrics_token.example) shows operators how to create it.
deploy/prometheus/metrics_token
!deploy/prometheus/metrics_token.example

# Agent worktrees (physical cleanup handled by merger post-merge)
.claude/worktrees/

# Frontend dependencies / build output
ui/node_modules/
ui/*.err.log
ui/*.out.log
ui/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# Orchestration / baseline scratch artifacts (not source)
.vite/
.baseline_pytest.txt
.bdp_baseline_failures.txt
.bdp*_workflow.js

# Personal (non-shared) Claude Code settings — shared config is settings.json
.claude/settings.local.json

# Internal scratch dirs (not source; manifest-excluded from public release)
BDP_REFORMED/

# Internal strategy artifacts — never committed, blacklisted from public release
# (mirrors release/public_manifest.yaml exclude globs *시장진단*/*로우리스크*/*전략*)
*시장진단*
*로우리스크*
*전략*

# Stray root lockfile — the JS project lives in ui/ (ui/package-lock.json is tracked)
/package-lock.json

# Python build outputs (python -m build / setuptools); regenerated, never committed.
# Keeps the runbook §2.2 clean-tree precondition intact after a Phase C build.
/dist/
*.egg-info/

# Tauri desktop backend sidecar — PyInstaller build artifacts (rebuilt at package time)
deploy/desktop/sidecar/dist/
deploy/desktop/sidecar/build/

# Serena MCP local project cache/config/memories — local tooling state, never committed
.serena/

# ── R1 위생 정비 (2026-07-02) ──────────────────────────────────────────
# LibreOffice/OpenOffice 스프레드시트 잠금 파일 (문서가 열려 있을 때 생성).
.~lock.*#

# 감사 세션 임시 probe/scratch 텍스트 파일.
_probe*.txt

# 내부 PoC 영업 인텔 — 실명 금융권 타겟 숏리스트 + 컨택.
# NEVER commit: 이 저장소는 공개 OSS(../secugent-core)로 추출된다. deny-by-default.
# 로컬 유지 + 저장소 밖 백업(R1 백업 zip)으로만 관리한다.
memory/

# 내부 PoC 계획 산출물 — 원가분석 + 실명 고객 계획.
# 위 memory/와 동일한 공개-유출 방지 근거. (시장진단/로우리스크/전략 HTML은
# 위쪽 기존 globs가 이미 커버.)
plans/Secugent_PoC_Plan_*.md
plans/*비용분석*.xlsx

# PoC 데모 런북(docs/demo/)의 임시 산출물 — 감사 저장소·시드 스크립트·출력 캡처.
# 데모마다 재생성되는 스크래치이므로 커밋하지 않는다(공개 추출 오염 방지).
demo-scratch/
